1
00:00:17,940 --> 00:00:21,260
♪The falling snow♪

2
00:00:21,620 --> 00:00:25,180
♪Is bitter cold♪

3
00:00:27,300 --> 00:00:29,980
♪My sigh♪

4
00:00:30,420 --> 00:00:34,460
♪Misted the path in front of me♪

5
00:00:36,620 --> 00:00:42,740
♪The moonlight knows my intention♪

6
00:00:44,860 --> 00:00:51,300
♪I just want to make a place
for me in your heart♪

7
00:00:53,820 --> 00:00:57,620
♪I laugh and I cry♪

8
00:00:58,340 --> 00:01:02,100
♪Quietly building a pond in my heart♪

9
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:06,780
♪I accept all the gifts from sorrow♪

10
00:01:07,580 --> 00:01:11,420
♪I can't let down my regrets♪

11
00:01:12,060 --> 00:01:15,860
♪I won't admit defeat♪

12
00:01:16,460 --> 00:01:20,260
♪I slowly chew
on the bitterness of life♪

13
00:01:20,980 --> 00:01:24,540
♪The fragrance remains the same
after the bleak winter♪

14
00:01:25,340 --> 00:01:29,540
♪Awaiting spring
to color the way back home♪

15
00:01:31,020 --> 00:01:36,340
[The Double]

16
00:01:36,340 --> 00:01:39,020
[Episode 30]

17
00:01:42,550 --> 00:01:43,110
Jiang Li.

18
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,030
Jiang Li,

19
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,800
your invitation card

20
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:49,360
has arrived.

21
00:01:50,030 --> 00:01:51,880
[To Jiang Li]
See where Mr. Shen has assigned you.

22
00:01:54,190 --> 00:01:54,830
This time,

23
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,000
the Court for Dependencies
has categorized the receptions.

24
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:59,000
I, Liu Xu, and Ye

25
00:01:59,080 --> 00:01:59,880
are assigned by the Ritual Ministry
to handle reception

26
00:02:00,750 --> 00:02:02,520
[Jiang Li assigned to Music Bureau]
along the way and at lodgings.

27
00:02:02,910 --> 00:02:04,030
Music Bureau?

28
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:07,110
Music Bureau?

29
00:02:09,390 --> 00:02:10,480
This isn't right.

30
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,270
You play the qin so well.

31
00:02:12,520 --> 00:02:13,960
Yet, they make you play ordinary pieces

32
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,200
with those musicians.

33
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,710
What's going on here?

34
00:02:17,110 --> 00:02:18,670
Which part does Mr. Shen oversee?

35
00:02:19,270 --> 00:02:21,920
Mr. Shen oversees everything.

36
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:24,390
He and those
at the Hanlin Academy are responsible

37
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,800
for compiling and organizing records
to be presented to Great Zhao.

38
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,480
This is the main focus
of the upcoming alliance.

39
00:02:31,870 --> 00:02:33,390
Oh, Shen Yurong.

40
00:02:33,830 --> 00:02:35,390
Why are you so afraid
of me getting close to you?

41
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:36,920
Are you afraid

42
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:38,520
I'll find something incriminating

43
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,800
or that Wanning will do something crazy
because of you

44
00:02:41,040 --> 00:02:42,710
that will reveal
something incriminating?

45
00:02:44,320 --> 00:02:46,080
It seems like you will be the first

46
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,240
to slip up.

47
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:50,240
[Cultivating Talents]
Yes.

48
00:02:51,200 --> 00:02:52,040
Are you sure?

49
00:02:52,040 --> 00:03:05,580
[Pursue Knowledge and Uphold Rules]

50
00:03:06,760 --> 00:03:08,800
Isn't this the top scorer
from the School of Integrity's exam?

51
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,480
What is she doing at Music Bureau?

52
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:11,550
Shouldn't she be doing a solo?

53
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,390
Second Lady Jiang,

54
00:03:17,960 --> 00:03:20,240
you cannot touch this qin.

55
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,550
It belongs to Ms. Xiao.

56
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,110
Where's mine?

57
00:03:32,390 --> 00:03:34,080
You're just like them, over there.

58
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,200
I want to see Ms. Xiao.

59
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,920
Who's looking for me?

60
00:03:54,270 --> 00:03:55,080
Ms. Xiao.

61
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:56,870
Earlier, I heard from Mr. Shen

62
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,800
that His Majesty wants
to hear me play solo.

63
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,800
But I'm being assigned to you.

64
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:03,870
With this arrangement,

65
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:05,800
isn't His Majesty's wish being ignored?

66
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,080
Second Lady Jiang,

67
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,550
I know you won the top spot in the exam

68
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:13,390
and gained His Majesty's admiration,
so you are proud and confident.

69
00:04:13,990 --> 00:04:16,230
Look at these musicians
from the Office of Instruction.

70
00:04:16,880 --> 00:04:18,880
They're all proud and confident too.

71
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:21,000
If you don't show some real skill,

72
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:23,080
you won't be able to convince them.

73
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:25,350
Mr. Shen knows
your qin skills are top-notch.

74
00:04:25,350 --> 00:04:26,680
That's why he wanted you to come

75
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:28,440
and set an example for them.

76
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:29,910
Second Lady Jiang,

77
00:04:30,150 --> 00:04:32,320
could it be that you can't put aside
your noble status?

78
00:05:14,620 --> 00:05:17,820
[Harmonious Melody]

79
00:05:26,520 --> 00:05:28,350
We cannot afford to fill in the numbers
with people who can't contribute

80
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,350
to the delegation to Great Yan.

81
00:05:30,710 --> 00:05:33,080
But Second Lady Jiang
has a special status.

82
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:34,590
So we can forgive this once.

83
00:05:35,470 --> 00:05:39,000
Today, I need everyone here to bear

84
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:41,350
with Second Lady Jiang

85
00:05:41,350 --> 00:05:42,960
until she catches up.

86
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:46,390
[Harmonious Melody]
These are the pieces you usually play.

87
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,560
I just received
the sheet music recently.

88
00:05:49,960 --> 00:05:52,440
So catching up
to everyone's level is challenging.

89
00:05:52,830 --> 00:05:54,830
But I don't want to drag everyone down

90
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:57,350
because I'm
the Grand Chancellor's daughter.

91
00:05:57,910 --> 00:05:58,640
Ms. Xiao,

92
00:05:59,030 --> 00:06:00,270
I'd like to practice alone

93
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:01,590
and catch up to everyone's level.

94
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:04,440
In that case, do as you wish.

95
00:06:04,680 --> 00:06:05,790
Practice alone then.

96
00:06:05,900 --> 00:06:11,500
[Harmonious Melody]

97
00:06:25,270 --> 00:06:27,910
Second Lady Jiang,
you need to practice diligently.

98
00:06:33,520 --> 00:06:34,710
If you fall behind,

99
00:06:35,030 --> 00:06:36,910
I can't afford

100
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,440
to have Mr. Shen blame me.

101
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,710
Ms. Xiao, don't worry.

102
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:41,320
I won't let you down.

103
00:06:41,830 --> 00:06:42,640
That's good to hear.

104
00:07:22,590 --> 00:07:23,520
Help!

105
00:07:24,230 --> 00:07:25,960
I... I've been bitten.

106
00:07:27,790 --> 00:07:28,640
What happened?

107
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:32,960
I... I found Jiuyue.

108
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:33,910
Where is Jiuyue?

109
00:07:35,230 --> 00:07:36,390
I wanted to go to the snake cave
to catch snakes.

110
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:39,230
He insisted on following me
and couldn't stop nagging.

111
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,640
He ended up getting bitten by a snake.

112
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,680
How dare you hit me?

113
00:07:47,710 --> 00:07:48,470
Where's the antidote?

114
00:07:49,710 --> 00:07:51,790
Trade your ten-year-old fine wine
for it.

115
00:07:51,790 --> 00:07:52,230
Fine.

116
00:08:01,830 --> 00:08:03,960
Wen Ji said
you were looking for me urgently.

117
00:08:05,470 --> 00:08:07,150
Your brother is leading
the Great Zhao delegation

118
00:08:07,150 --> 00:08:08,080
to meet with Great Yan
for an alliance soon.

119
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,470
You'll be reunited with him then.

120
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:11,560
That's great news.

121
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:14,520
King Cheng opposes the alliance
between Great Zhao and Great Yan.

122
00:08:15,270 --> 00:08:16,910
He will definitely disrupt the alliance,

123
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:18,200
which could endanger you.

124
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:20,030
During this time,
you should stay at the Duke's Residence.

125
00:08:20,030 --> 00:08:20,830
You'll be safer here.

126
00:08:23,790 --> 00:08:27,080
Is that why you called me here?

127
00:08:28,150 --> 00:08:29,150
Are you really that concerned about me?

128
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,080
There's one more thing.

129
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,440
What is it?

130
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:33,630
I need you to help two people.

131
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:35,750
One has amnesia,
and the other is disfigured by a knife.

132
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,440
Oh, Xiao Heng.

133
00:08:38,470 --> 00:08:40,590
Do you see everyone

134
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:41,830
as pawns?

135
00:08:41,830 --> 00:08:42,710
After it's done,

136
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:45,400
you can have all the wine you want.

137
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:46,960
Wine?

138
00:08:48,710 --> 00:08:50,080
That's two lives we're talking about.

139
00:08:52,230 --> 00:08:53,510
It can't be that easy.

140
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,800
What do you propose?

141
00:08:55,510 --> 00:08:56,230
Tell me,

142
00:08:56,510 --> 00:08:59,470
for who do you want to save those two?

143
00:09:02,750 --> 00:09:03,990
I can see you struggling to answer me.

144
00:09:04,990 --> 00:09:08,230
Is it for Second Lady Jiang again?

145
00:09:09,040 --> 00:09:11,350
Will you save them or not?

146
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:15,110
Is this how you ask for help?

147
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,470
What do you want me to do?

148
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:19,320
I want...

149
00:09:20,470 --> 00:09:21,470
I want you to accompany me
to catch spiders.

150
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:23,920
Show me your sincerity.

151
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:40,920
I thought you wanted to catch spiders.

152
00:09:41,470 --> 00:09:42,110
Are we catching them here?

153
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:42,830
Yes, we are.

154
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,630
I'm not here to swim with you.

155
00:09:48,350 --> 00:09:50,350
If we want to catch the water spiders,
we have to catch them from the water.

156
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:52,990
Wait here.

157
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:56,590
Keep an eye on her.

158
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:57,800
Yes, My Lord.

159
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,230
Why are you back?

160
00:10:06,590 --> 00:10:08,110
She was undressing while talking.

161
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,320
If I stay,

162
00:10:09,590 --> 00:10:11,750
she'll tell the Great Zhao's emperor
that she was molested.

163
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:33,510
Xiao Heng!

164
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:40,680
It turns out you truly care about me.

165
00:10:40,870 --> 00:10:41,750
If you don't want to save them,

166
00:10:41,800 --> 00:10:43,040
you don't have to toy with me like this.

167
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,040
I...

168
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:52,560
Xiao Heng,

169
00:10:53,350 --> 00:10:54,510
haven't you toyed with me before?

170
00:11:08,990 --> 00:11:10,160
The arrow is poisoned.

171
00:11:10,590 --> 00:11:11,590
Only I can cure it.

172
00:11:14,990 --> 00:11:16,320
If you want me to save you,

173
00:11:17,630 --> 00:11:20,400
you have to offer yourself.

174
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:22,960
I don't indulge in romance.

175
00:11:24,470 --> 00:11:25,440
I don't care if you'll save me or not.

176
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,700
Is your refusal to indulge in romance

177
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:32,490
only meant for me?

178
00:11:32,700 --> 00:11:34,420
So you're not going
to save those two people then.

179
00:11:37,340 --> 00:11:38,730
I can save them

180
00:11:39,580 --> 00:11:42,610
as long as you offer your life
in return.

181
00:11:42,890 --> 00:11:44,100
Jiuyue, stop messing around.

182
00:11:44,530 --> 00:11:47,580
Fine, I'll stop.

183
00:11:49,700 --> 00:11:50,650
About those two,

184
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:52,180
I don't care about saving them.

185
00:11:54,940 --> 00:11:55,490
Jiuyue.

186
00:11:58,010 --> 00:11:58,610
Lu Ji,

187
00:11:59,460 --> 00:12:00,250
keep her safe.

188
00:12:00,730 --> 00:12:01,250
Yes, My Lord.

189
00:12:10,900 --> 00:12:11,820
[Hanlin Academy]

190
00:12:11,820 --> 00:12:12,650
Mr. Shen,

191
00:12:13,100 --> 00:12:14,460
[Honoring the Wisdom of Sages]
Mr. Shen, this is the budget

192
00:12:14,460 --> 00:12:15,940
for meals submitted
by the Court for Dependencies.

193
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:17,270
Please review it.

194
00:12:17,270 --> 00:12:18,100
[Banquet Expenses Overview]

195
00:12:18,270 --> 00:12:20,740
Mr. Shen, this is the repertoire list
for the Music Bureau.

196
00:12:20,950 --> 00:12:22,070
Please review this too.

197
00:12:24,150 --> 00:12:24,790
Thank you.

198
00:12:25,500 --> 00:12:27,500
The alliance with Great Yan is
of great significance.

199
00:12:27,910 --> 00:12:30,270
I'll need both of you
to take on more responsibilities.

200
00:12:30,460 --> 00:12:33,460
Please inform me promptly of any issues.

201
00:12:33,860 --> 00:12:34,460
All right.

202
00:12:38,390 --> 00:12:40,740
Ms. Xiao, do you have something to say?

203
00:12:41,030 --> 00:12:43,700
It's nothing urgent.

204
00:12:44,030 --> 00:12:45,340
It's just that Second Lady Jiang

205
00:12:45,820 --> 00:12:47,910
has been absent from rehearsals
for two days.

206
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:49,790
She said she's not well

207
00:12:49,790 --> 00:12:51,220
and might need a few more days of rest.

208
00:12:51,910 --> 00:12:53,190
Resting is understandable.

209
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:56,550
But she's unfamiliar
with the new repertoire.

210
00:12:56,740 --> 00:12:58,340
If we wait for her to recover,

211
00:12:58,950 --> 00:13:01,910
she might hold back
the Music Bureau's performance.

212
00:13:02,190 --> 00:13:03,550
If her health can't handle it,

213
00:13:04,390 --> 00:13:05,790
it's better for her to get proper rest.

214
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:35,910
Ye, why are you here?

215
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:38,310
Xiao Deyin said you're not well.

216
00:13:38,460 --> 00:13:39,580
So I brought medicine for you.

217
00:13:40,390 --> 00:13:41,390
Thank you, Ye.

218
00:13:47,340 --> 00:13:48,420
But how did you get sick

219
00:13:48,770 --> 00:13:50,300
just from practicing the qin?

220
00:13:50,580 --> 00:13:51,300
Ye,

221
00:13:52,130 --> 00:13:53,700
I remember you mentioned before

222
00:13:54,060 --> 00:13:55,730
that His Majesty wanted to hear me play

223
00:13:55,730 --> 00:13:57,060
"Spring Fading
into White Pear Blossoms."

224
00:13:57,370 --> 00:13:58,130
Yes, that's correct.

225
00:13:58,420 --> 00:14:02,180
But why did Mr. Shen place me
in the Music Bureau?

226
00:14:02,530 --> 00:14:03,300
He said he hoped you would inspire

227
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:04,980
the Music Bureau to work harder.

228
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:07,180
But following Mr. Shen's instructions,

229
00:14:07,180 --> 00:14:08,580
Ms. Xiao gave me new sheet music.

230
00:14:10,130 --> 00:14:11,850
Instead of highlighting my strengths,

231
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:13,420
it exposed my weaknesses.

232
00:14:13,940 --> 00:14:15,250
It's my fault
for being too busy recently

233
00:14:15,420 --> 00:14:16,370
that I overlooked your situation.

234
00:14:16,940 --> 00:14:18,420
I'll go and see Mr. Shen shortly.

235
00:14:18,940 --> 00:14:20,730
I really don't want to stay
in the Music Bureau.

236
00:14:21,460 --> 00:14:23,220
If you really want to help me,

237
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:25,530
I have a solution.

238
00:14:35,780 --> 00:14:36,660
[Grand Ancestral Ceremony]

239
00:14:39,650 --> 00:14:40,980
Your thorough arrangement puts my mind

240
00:14:41,370 --> 00:14:42,300
at ease, Official Shen.

241
00:14:42,490 --> 00:14:43,370
There's something

242
00:14:43,940 --> 00:14:45,340
I shouldn't trouble Your Majesty with.

243
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:47,420
But it concerns Jiang Li,
the daughter of the Secretariat Director.

244
00:14:47,940 --> 00:14:49,220
I dare not make decisions on my own.

245
00:14:50,850 --> 00:14:51,420
Go on.

246
00:14:51,610 --> 00:14:53,850
Your Majesty wants Second Lady Jiang
to represent Great Yan

247
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:54,940
and showcase her musical skills.

248
00:14:55,340 --> 00:14:56,820
However, this alliance is different
from the Entry Exam.

249
00:14:57,100 --> 00:14:59,340
The performance affects more
than just the individual.

250
00:14:59,980 --> 00:15:02,850
She has not been practicing
for several months since the exam

251
00:15:03,180 --> 00:15:04,610
and has gone through many incidents,

252
00:15:04,700 --> 00:15:06,060
making her qin skills rusty.

253
00:15:06,180 --> 00:15:07,730
I initially thought of arranging for her

254
00:15:07,730 --> 00:15:08,730
to practice and recover
at the Music Bureau.

255
00:15:09,100 --> 00:15:10,650
But then she fell ill unexpectedly.

256
00:15:10,850 --> 00:15:12,130
Forcing her

257
00:15:12,340 --> 00:15:13,820
might not only be detrimental
to the alliance

258
00:15:13,890 --> 00:15:16,730
but also make the Secretariat Director feel
that my arrangements are inadequate.

259
00:15:16,890 --> 00:15:18,890
Official Shen, what do you suggest then?

260
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:21,250
Let Second Lady Jiang focus
on recovering.

261
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:23,650
[Govern the People, Serve Heaven]
Your Majesty. Mr. Shen.

262
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:26,220
After hearing about my cousin's illness,
I went to visit her.

263
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:28,820
Ms. Xiao gave Jiang Li a music piece
that the musicians know well.

264
00:15:29,060 --> 00:15:31,010
But it's her first time playing it.

265
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:32,770
Jiang Li pushed herself
to practice day and night

266
00:15:33,010 --> 00:15:35,060
to avoid dragging the Music Bureau,
which led to her falling ill.

267
00:15:35,130 --> 00:15:35,890
Despite that,

268
00:15:36,060 --> 00:15:37,130
she continued
to practice even while sick,

269
00:15:37,580 --> 00:15:39,100
showing her dedication.

270
00:15:39,300 --> 00:15:40,580
This alliance is crucial.

271
00:15:40,890 --> 00:15:42,130
Given Jiang Li's current condition,

272
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:43,530
even if she doesn't practice new pieces

273
00:15:43,650 --> 00:15:44,370
and only plays her familiar

274
00:15:44,370 --> 00:15:45,730
"Spring Fading
into White Pear Blossoms",

275
00:15:46,130 --> 00:15:47,370
she might not reach the level
she had during the Entry Exam

276
00:15:47,370 --> 00:15:48,940
when she recovers.

277
00:15:49,180 --> 00:15:50,180
Your Majesty, please consider this.

278
00:15:51,420 --> 00:15:53,100
Jiang Li just needs a few days of rest

279
00:15:53,100 --> 00:15:54,010
to recover from her illness.

280
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:55,850
While her condition may not be
as good as during the exams,

281
00:15:56,370 --> 00:15:57,850
Jiang Li is talented and devoted.

282
00:15:58,340 --> 00:16:00,220
If we're not confined
to the exam pieces,

283
00:16:00,370 --> 00:16:03,180
perhaps she could collaborate
with the Hanlin scholars

284
00:16:03,490 --> 00:16:04,980
to create a new performance style,

285
00:16:04,980 --> 00:16:06,730
highlighting each other's strengths
and covering weaknesses,

286
00:16:07,180 --> 00:16:10,180
which could impress
the Great Zhao delegation.

287
00:16:10,420 --> 00:16:11,340
What kind of plan is this?

288
00:16:11,340 --> 00:16:12,580
Official Shen, calm down.

289
00:16:13,490 --> 00:16:15,370
Official Ye's proposal is intriguing.

290
00:16:16,420 --> 00:16:17,650
Innovating

291
00:16:17,820 --> 00:16:19,820
has always been your forte.

292
00:16:20,100 --> 00:16:22,010
Official Shen,
you might as well give it a try.

293
00:16:23,890 --> 00:16:24,730
- Yes, Your Majesty.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

294
00:16:29,100 --> 00:16:31,260
[Govern the People, Serve Heaven]

295
00:16:41,820 --> 00:16:42,610
Your pawn

296
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:44,650
always involves me
like this unnecessarily.

297
00:16:44,820 --> 00:16:46,100
That's her talent.

298
00:16:47,420 --> 00:16:48,300
So, tell me.

299
00:16:48,490 --> 00:16:49,580
What does she ultimately want to do?

300
00:16:49,730 --> 00:16:51,180
Perhaps Your Majesty

301
00:16:51,300 --> 00:16:52,250
should ask Second Lady Jiang directly?

302
00:16:53,850 --> 00:16:56,820
I guess there are still things
that even you can't figure out.

303
00:16:58,220 --> 00:16:58,770
Interesting.

304
00:17:01,180 --> 00:17:08,060
[Hanlin Academy]

305
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:16,140
Isn't this Second Lady Jiang?

306
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:20,330
Are you here at the Hanlin Academy

307
00:17:20,420 --> 00:17:22,290
to catch the eye
of some young master again?

308
00:17:22,530 --> 00:17:23,810
I've told you before.

309
00:17:23,860 --> 00:17:26,050
If you miss me,
you won't find anyone better.

310
00:17:26,380 --> 00:17:27,860
Your outfit today looks nice.

311
00:17:28,570 --> 00:17:30,180
Is it to impress someone?

312
00:17:30,290 --> 00:17:32,140
I... I'm here at the Hanlin Academy

313
00:17:32,140 --> 00:17:33,570
to participate
in compiling the classics.

314
00:17:33,570 --> 00:17:34,810
As for you,

315
00:17:35,250 --> 00:17:36,290
what about you?

316
00:17:36,290 --> 00:17:37,730
Mr. Shen summoned me.

317
00:17:37,940 --> 00:17:39,220
Mr. Shen?

318
00:17:40,380 --> 00:17:42,180
You two just caused a scene
in front of His Majesty.

319
00:17:42,180 --> 00:17:43,250
And now you dare to interact?

320
00:17:43,380 --> 00:17:44,730
Aren't you afraid of gossip?

321
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:48,420
A clear conscience fears no slander.

322
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:49,730
Impressive.

323
00:17:58,530 --> 00:17:59,900
Is there anything I can do for you,
Mr. Shen?

324
00:17:59,900 --> 00:18:01,380
Didn't your cousin tell you?

325
00:18:01,660 --> 00:18:03,570
Since Mr. Shen is in charge
of this matter,

326
00:18:03,860 --> 00:18:05,290
it's only appropriate for me
to hear from you.

327
00:18:05,620 --> 00:18:07,770
His Majesty
has approved Ye Shijie's proposal.

328
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:09,660
Who would you like to perform with here

329
00:18:10,940 --> 00:18:12,220
at the Hanlin Academy?

330
00:18:14,660 --> 00:18:16,490
Naturally, you

331
00:18:17,530 --> 00:18:18,330
have the final say.

332
00:18:21,050 --> 00:18:22,050
In that case,

333
00:18:22,980 --> 00:18:23,980
it will be Zhao Qi.

334
00:18:24,220 --> 00:18:25,900
You seemed quite close just now.

335
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:27,980
It saves time in getting acquainted.

336
00:18:28,180 --> 00:18:29,180
Can you choose someone else?

337
00:18:29,460 --> 00:18:30,730
Didn't you say I have the final say?

338
00:18:31,140 --> 00:18:32,660
Since you insist,

339
00:18:33,490 --> 00:18:34,620
I'll follow your arrangement.

340
00:18:35,490 --> 00:18:37,050
I'll go and talk to Zhao Qi

341
00:18:37,180 --> 00:18:38,090
and start rehearsals tomorrow.

342
00:18:47,770 --> 00:18:48,530
Bai Xue,

343
00:18:49,380 --> 00:18:50,700
I remember my cousin, Jia'er,

344
00:18:50,700 --> 00:18:52,380
gave me some silk and satin before.

345
00:18:53,380 --> 00:18:55,770
There was
a handwoven Yunjin handkerchief.

346
00:18:56,250 --> 00:18:57,380
Bring it to me later.

347
00:18:58,140 --> 00:19:00,460
My Lady,
you should have used it earlier.

348
00:19:00,700 --> 00:19:01,810
Such good material

349
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:03,460
should complement someone
as beautiful as you.

350
00:19:04,810 --> 00:19:06,250
It's not for my personal use.

351
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:07,530
Then what is it for?

352
00:19:07,700 --> 00:19:09,180
To please others.

353
00:19:15,770 --> 00:19:17,460
I was actually looking forward
to your performance.

354
00:19:17,810 --> 00:19:18,730
Now

355
00:19:19,050 --> 00:19:20,420
I've become a part of this drama.

356
00:19:21,570 --> 00:19:23,140
I know you don't want to play with me.

357
00:19:23,730 --> 00:19:25,010
So do I.

358
00:19:25,530 --> 00:19:28,660
So go talk to Mr. Shen and decline it.

359
00:19:28,660 --> 00:19:29,330
Me?

360
00:19:29,810 --> 00:19:30,290
Yes.

361
00:19:30,490 --> 00:19:31,290
Forget it.

362
00:19:31,620 --> 00:19:32,810
If I offend Mr. Shen,

363
00:19:32,980 --> 00:19:34,900
can I still stay at Hanlin Academy?

364
00:19:35,250 --> 00:19:36,090
Besides,

365
00:19:36,490 --> 00:19:37,290
this is also an opportunity

366
00:19:37,290 --> 00:19:38,730
to appear in front of His Majesty.

367
00:19:39,220 --> 00:19:40,090
Why would I want to decline it?

368
00:19:40,380 --> 00:19:41,290
You must go.

369
00:19:42,250 --> 00:19:44,940
Otherwise, your parents will find out

370
00:19:44,940 --> 00:19:45,810
about the lady you...

371
00:19:47,460 --> 00:19:47,860
So are you going or not?

372
00:19:48,010 --> 00:19:48,700
Are you threatening me?

373
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:49,570
Not just a threat.

374
00:19:49,980 --> 00:19:50,730
There's also a temptation.

375
00:19:51,980 --> 00:19:54,570
I heard you've been searching
for this Yunjin handkerchief.

376
00:19:54,940 --> 00:19:56,420
Today, I brought you a top-notch one.

377
00:19:57,050 --> 00:19:57,620
Take a look.

378
00:19:58,090 --> 00:20:00,090
Will it catch the eye
of your sweetheart?

379
00:20:03,500 --> 00:20:04,090
Let me take a look.

380
00:20:09,940 --> 00:20:12,050
This Yunjin handkerchief is from Luyang.

381
00:20:12,530 --> 00:20:14,010
It's hard to find in the capital.

382
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:17,020
How did you get it?

383
00:20:17,020 --> 00:20:18,570
My maternal grandmother's family
is from Luyang.

384
00:20:24,250 --> 00:20:25,010
Then

385
00:20:25,460 --> 00:20:27,250
I'll reluctantly cooperate

386
00:20:28,260 --> 00:20:29,050
with you for now.

387
00:20:38,740 --> 00:20:41,140
Please replace me with someone else
for Second Lady Jiang.

388
00:20:41,900 --> 00:20:43,090
We've discussed
a marriage proposal before.

389
00:20:43,330 --> 00:20:44,570
If we perform together,

390
00:20:44,900 --> 00:20:46,050
it will inevitably draw criticism.

391
00:20:46,050 --> 00:20:47,220
If you have a clear conscience,

392
00:20:47,730 --> 00:20:49,180
why bother about idle talk?

393
00:20:50,530 --> 00:20:52,050
Even if I have a clear conscience,

394
00:20:53,330 --> 00:20:54,900
rumors can still be dangerous.

395
00:20:55,980 --> 00:20:57,420
It's a tribute to Great Zhao.

396
00:20:58,090 --> 00:20:59,770
I hope you can set
aside personal emotions

397
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:01,010
and prioritize the bigger picture.

398
00:21:01,490 --> 00:21:02,290
Mr. Shen, please.

399
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:04,090
Mr. Shen...

400
00:21:14,570 --> 00:21:15,530
We don't have much time left.

401
00:21:15,980 --> 00:21:16,730
Let's go inside and rehearse.

402
00:21:25,740 --> 00:21:28,620
[Hanlin Academy]

403
00:21:35,140 --> 00:21:38,900
[Honoring the Wisdom of Sages]

404
00:21:42,090 --> 00:21:42,730
Yurong,

405
00:21:43,810 --> 00:21:45,730
they're not even rehearsing.

406
00:21:46,570 --> 00:21:48,090
What are they doing inside?

407
00:21:52,260 --> 00:21:53,810
I'll try to decline as you suggested.

408
00:21:53,980 --> 00:21:54,740
But it's not working.

409
00:21:56,770 --> 00:21:58,420
Put another act for me.

410
00:21:59,460 --> 00:22:01,260
What? Again?

411
00:22:01,660 --> 00:22:04,500
Does your sweetheart like
that handkerchief?

412
00:22:05,700 --> 00:22:07,500
I have even better ones.

413
00:22:07,770 --> 00:22:10,290
I'll bring them tomorrow.
You can let her choose.

414
00:22:12,090 --> 00:22:13,660
Just this once, no more next time.

415
00:22:13,700 --> 00:22:14,290
All right.

416
00:22:15,700 --> 00:22:16,180
Go home.

417
00:22:17,130 --> 00:22:17,660
All right.

418
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:19,500
[Honoring the Wisdom of Sages]

419
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:20,130
Jiang Li,

420
00:22:20,570 --> 00:22:21,850
are you doing this on purpose?

421
00:22:22,020 --> 00:22:22,900
From the beginning,

422
00:22:23,050 --> 00:22:24,180
is this all your scheme?

423
00:22:24,420 --> 00:22:25,290
Scheme?

424
00:22:25,660 --> 00:22:26,940
What scheme could I have?

425
00:22:27,020 --> 00:22:28,610
It was Mr. Shen who asked me to come.

426
00:22:29,500 --> 00:22:31,130
How would I know he wanted me
to work with you?

427
00:22:31,500 --> 00:22:32,530
You don't know?

428
00:22:32,770 --> 00:22:34,290
Stop pretending already.

429
00:22:34,730 --> 00:22:36,260
I made it clear to you earlier.

430
00:22:36,260 --> 00:22:37,220
We're not suitable.

431
00:22:37,570 --> 00:22:39,090
Now that you're getting close like this,

432
00:22:39,090 --> 00:22:40,940
anyone who doesn't know would think
we're getting back together.

433
00:22:41,420 --> 00:22:42,900
How can I get married
in the future, huh?

434
00:22:43,020 --> 00:22:44,980
Do you think
you're the only one who minds?

435
00:22:45,330 --> 00:22:46,900
There's nothing we can do now.

436
00:22:47,220 --> 00:22:48,460
I don't have anything
to say to you anymore.

437
00:22:48,460 --> 00:22:49,730
Me neither.

438
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:07,220
Mr. Shen, I apologize for that.

439
00:23:13,530 --> 00:23:14,370
Go home first.

440
00:23:15,460 --> 00:23:16,370
Yurong.

441
00:23:16,420 --> 00:23:17,050
I said, go.

442
00:23:35,660 --> 00:23:36,530
Second Lady Jiang,

443
00:23:40,500 --> 00:23:41,460
what happened here?

444
00:23:42,020 --> 00:23:43,740
Weren't you two rehearsing
just fine earlier?

445
00:23:44,010 --> 00:23:45,660
Did you do this on purpose, Mr. Shen?

446
00:23:46,660 --> 00:23:47,180
On purpose?

447
00:23:47,460 --> 00:23:49,250
I overheard the conversation
between you and Zhao Qi

448
00:23:49,250 --> 00:23:50,290
this afternoon.

449
00:23:50,570 --> 00:23:52,330
It seemed like
you deliberately brought someone

450
00:23:52,330 --> 00:23:53,860
who had a previous engagement with me

451
00:23:53,860 --> 00:23:56,700
to stir up trouble and make me pull out.

452
00:23:56,770 --> 00:23:58,290
Second Lady Jiang, you're mistaken.

453
00:23:58,660 --> 00:24:01,660
Zhao Qi is a highly educated person
among the scholars.

454
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:03,500
If I didn't do this,

455
00:24:03,740 --> 00:24:05,900
how could I match up
to your deliberate suggestion

456
00:24:07,300 --> 00:24:10,130
to have Official Ye propose ideas
in front of the emperor?

457
00:24:13,220 --> 00:24:14,260
Mr. Shen, you should choose
your words carefully.

458
00:24:14,580 --> 00:24:17,220
You were the one who tried to get rid
of me in front of the emperor first.

459
00:24:17,260 --> 00:24:18,940
You were the one who was absent
because of illness first.

460
00:24:18,940 --> 00:24:21,090
I don't know
how did I ever offend you, Mr. Shen.

461
00:24:21,420 --> 00:24:22,700
You've been suspicious

462
00:24:22,780 --> 00:24:24,420
and targeting me all along.

463
00:24:25,020 --> 00:24:26,180
Helping with the alliance

464
00:24:26,460 --> 00:24:27,700
is for the benefit of Great Yan

465
00:24:28,020 --> 00:24:29,500
and adds glory to the Jiang family.

466
00:24:30,220 --> 00:24:31,900
So, I won't give up.

467
00:24:32,580 --> 00:24:34,370
If you continue
to make things difficult for me,

468
00:24:34,660 --> 00:24:36,900
it will reflect poorly on Great Yan.

469
00:24:43,220 --> 00:24:43,850
Tomorrow,

470
00:24:46,730 --> 00:24:48,050
I'll find another person for you.

471
00:25:02,330 --> 00:25:02,860
Mr. Zhao.

472
00:25:03,420 --> 00:25:04,010
Mr. Du.

473
00:25:04,220 --> 00:25:05,770
Can we talk?

474
00:25:05,860 --> 00:25:06,460
What is it?

475
00:25:07,250 --> 00:25:09,420
Mr. Shen assigned me to rehearse

476
00:25:09,770 --> 00:25:10,700
with Second Lady Jiang.

477
00:25:10,700 --> 00:25:11,940
[Honor the Way]
Congratulations, Mr. Du.

478
00:25:12,420 --> 00:25:13,980
This alliance will bring honor.

479
00:25:14,140 --> 00:25:15,140
If the emperor is pleased,

480
00:25:15,220 --> 00:25:17,420
it will be beneficial for your career.

481
00:25:17,660 --> 00:25:19,420
It looks good on the surface,

482
00:25:20,010 --> 00:25:21,380
but

483
00:25:21,380 --> 00:25:23,250
why did you decline Mr. Shen?

484
00:25:29,860 --> 00:25:31,980
I'm telling you this
because you're my friend.

485
00:25:32,980 --> 00:25:35,330
What seems good on the surface

486
00:25:36,220 --> 00:25:39,460
often hides underlying tensions.

487
00:25:40,090 --> 00:25:40,810
How so?

488
00:25:42,460 --> 00:25:43,290
Let me put it this way.

489
00:25:43,530 --> 00:25:44,810
Jiang Li is really evil.

490
00:25:45,050 --> 00:25:46,140
She eats people.

491
00:25:47,570 --> 00:25:48,620
What? She eats people?

492
00:25:49,010 --> 00:25:50,290
It was just a metaphor.

493
00:25:50,810 --> 00:25:52,090
I just want to let you know

494
00:25:52,290 --> 00:25:54,570
that sometimes things appear
to be a blessing,

495
00:25:54,700 --> 00:25:58,290
but it's actually a bottomless abyss
beneath their feet.

496
00:25:58,810 --> 00:25:59,860
What should I do then?

497
00:26:00,290 --> 00:26:02,620
Jiang Li is coming to rehearse
with me tonight.

498
00:26:03,900 --> 00:26:04,530
Mr. Zhao,

499
00:26:04,810 --> 00:26:06,980
could you advise me?

500
00:26:07,050 --> 00:26:08,530
Mr. Shen is kind and understanding.

501
00:26:08,700 --> 00:26:10,660
He changed his decision for me.

502
00:26:11,140 --> 00:26:13,380
If you have any difficulties,

503
00:26:13,460 --> 00:26:14,940
and with many scholars in Hanlin,

504
00:26:15,220 --> 00:26:16,490
there is bound to be someone
who has no difficulties, right?

505
00:26:22,570 --> 00:26:23,770
I understand it now.

506
00:26:23,900 --> 00:26:24,980
Thank you, Mr. Zhao.

507
00:26:33,730 --> 00:26:34,290
Go

508
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:37,770
and ask Jiang Li
for the pearl necklace she promised.

509
00:26:37,940 --> 00:26:38,380
Yes.

510
00:26:38,380 --> 00:26:41,500
[Honor the Way]

511
00:26:46,770 --> 00:26:47,660
Mr. Cheng, please come this way.

512
00:26:47,770 --> 00:26:48,290
All right.

513
00:26:48,980 --> 00:26:50,090
You can leave these here.

514
00:26:50,330 --> 00:26:51,460
Then I'll go and see them tomorrow.

515
00:26:51,700 --> 00:26:52,490
I'll wait for you.

516
00:26:52,660 --> 00:26:53,460
All right.

517
00:26:53,940 --> 00:26:54,660
Liu, take care.

518
00:26:54,660 --> 00:26:55,180
Let's go.

519
00:27:07,730 --> 00:27:08,330
What's wrong?

520
00:27:08,730 --> 00:27:09,730
I was craving cold drinks last night

521
00:27:09,940 --> 00:27:11,220
and mixed ice cubes in water.

522
00:27:11,330 --> 00:27:13,050
Now my stomach hurts terribly.

523
00:27:13,330 --> 00:27:14,900
Come, I'll take you to the physician.

524
00:27:15,180 --> 00:27:16,220
No, no, no. I can't.

525
00:27:16,700 --> 00:27:17,980
I can't hold it.

526
00:27:18,940 --> 00:27:19,460
I've already soiled

527
00:27:22,570 --> 00:27:23,460
my trousers.

528
00:27:26,220 --> 00:27:27,660
You...

529
00:27:27,660 --> 00:27:28,330
Mr. Shen,

530
00:27:28,770 --> 00:27:30,660
I'll go back first to freshen up
and change my clothes.

531
00:27:31,050 --> 00:27:32,250
Then I'll see the physician.

532
00:27:32,420 --> 00:27:33,490
I might not be able

533
00:27:33,490 --> 00:27:34,530
to attend tonight's rehearsal.

534
00:27:34,660 --> 00:27:36,530
I hope you can keep this a secret

535
00:27:36,770 --> 00:27:38,220
and protect my reputation.

536
00:27:38,530 --> 00:27:39,380
I'll take my leave now.

537
00:27:45,660 --> 00:27:47,780
[Hanlin Academy]

538
00:28:11,490 --> 00:28:12,420
Second Lady Jiang,

539
00:28:13,220 --> 00:28:14,050
what happened to you...

540
00:28:14,250 --> 00:28:15,810
My carriage broke down on the way.

541
00:28:16,530 --> 00:28:17,460
I had to walk over.

542
00:28:17,460 --> 00:28:18,290
Sorry for being late.

543
00:28:19,220 --> 00:28:19,940
I can begin now.

544
00:28:20,570 --> 00:28:21,980
I found Mr. Du, a talented scholar

545
00:28:22,140 --> 00:28:24,380
among the Hanlin students,
to perform with you.

546
00:28:24,620 --> 00:28:25,660
Unfortunately,

547
00:28:25,860 --> 00:28:26,770
- he is...
- It doesn't matter.

548
00:28:28,010 --> 00:28:30,900
I know no one wants to perform with me.

549
00:28:34,530 --> 00:28:36,860
I'm all soaked but end up with nothing.

550
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:39,490
Mr. Shen, I must look foolish.

551
00:28:41,250 --> 00:28:41,810
Jiang Li,

552
00:28:42,860 --> 00:28:44,460
everything I said earlier was true.

553
00:28:44,860 --> 00:28:46,490
I had no intention
of playing tricks on you.

554
00:28:47,730 --> 00:28:49,250
He really isn't feeling well today.

555
00:28:52,290 --> 00:28:53,860
I'm not blaming you.

556
00:28:54,530 --> 00:28:55,860
I'm blaming myself.

557
00:28:58,700 --> 00:28:59,770
For so many years,

558
00:28:59,980 --> 00:29:01,530
I've carried the stigma
of matricide and fratricide.

559
00:29:01,900 --> 00:29:03,570
I was questioned by Eldest Princess
about my identity,

560
00:29:04,140 --> 00:29:05,980
with my mother gone mad,
and my father's absence,

561
00:29:06,570 --> 00:29:08,730
it's no wonder you avoided me
before this.

562
00:29:08,900 --> 00:29:09,730
At this assembly,

563
00:29:09,810 --> 00:29:11,620
I just wanted
to make a name for myself.

564
00:29:12,330 --> 00:29:13,090
I didn't expect

565
00:29:13,810 --> 00:29:15,050
that all of you

566
00:29:15,570 --> 00:29:17,490
already see me as a jinx.

567
00:29:18,140 --> 00:29:19,050
Take shelter here first.

568
00:29:20,140 --> 00:29:21,010
Leave when the rain stops.

569
00:29:29,250 --> 00:29:31,180
Put this on for now.
You can leave when the rain lets up.

570
00:29:39,330 --> 00:29:41,660
This is "Shuo Yuan" by Liu Xiang
from the Han dynasty.

571
00:29:42,380 --> 00:29:42,980
Exactly.

572
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:47,620
My dear, you should include "Shuo Yuan".

573
00:29:48,860 --> 00:29:50,250
My father used to say

574
00:29:50,250 --> 00:29:51,700
he was very interested in "Shuo Yuan".

575
00:29:52,140 --> 00:29:54,250
But most of it has been lost now.

576
00:29:54,810 --> 00:29:57,420
He said if someone could collect
and recompile it,

577
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:59,220
it would be a great merit.

578
00:30:01,380 --> 00:30:04,060
[Shuo Yuan]

579
00:30:05,050 --> 00:30:07,290
I remember it has twenty volumes.

580
00:30:07,700 --> 00:30:09,530
But most of it is lost.

581
00:30:10,090 --> 00:30:12,250
I didn't expect you to collect so much.

582
00:30:12,460 --> 00:30:13,940
It took quite an effort

583
00:30:14,570 --> 00:30:15,980
to gather these fragments.

584
00:30:16,220 --> 00:30:17,940
I plan to compile them into a book.

585
00:30:18,220 --> 00:30:18,730
This way, this classic

586
00:30:18,730 --> 00:30:20,730
can be passed down through generations

587
00:30:21,290 --> 00:30:22,220
and benefit future generations.

588
00:30:25,290 --> 00:30:26,570
Mr. Shen, you're really amazing.

589
00:30:27,420 --> 00:30:28,700
Second Lady Jiang, you're too kind.

590
00:30:30,050 --> 00:30:30,810
But you, on the other hand,

591
00:30:31,140 --> 00:30:32,460
can recognize "Shuo Yuan"

592
00:30:32,980 --> 00:30:34,420
with just these fragments.

593
00:30:35,220 --> 00:30:36,860
That's quite surprising.

594
00:30:38,860 --> 00:30:40,620
Mr. Shen, you're different
from what I imagined.

595
00:30:40,980 --> 00:30:41,900
How so?

596
00:30:42,380 --> 00:30:43,250
I thought

597
00:30:43,290 --> 00:30:46,700
those favored by the emperor
would be skilled in social interactions.

598
00:30:47,140 --> 00:30:49,220
I didn't expect you
to rely on your knowledge.

599
00:30:49,490 --> 00:30:50,770
You truly have remarkable qualities.

600
00:30:50,980 --> 00:30:52,700
I'm just following the principles
from the text.

601
00:30:53,330 --> 00:30:56,010
A loyal minister should follow
the six righteous paths.

602
00:30:56,860 --> 00:30:59,250
Being humble and diligent,
progressing daily in virtue,

603
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:02,490
promoting the worthy tirelessly,
and upholding the law.

604
00:31:02,940 --> 00:31:05,810
The text says there are six righteous
and six unrighteous paths.

605
00:31:06,570 --> 00:31:08,980
Following the righteous brings honor,
while the other brings disgrace.

606
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:12,050
A virtuous minister follows
the righteous paths and avoids the other,

607
00:31:12,460 --> 00:31:14,290
thus ensuring stability
and people are well-governed.

608
00:31:17,620 --> 00:31:18,730
Mr. Shen,

609
00:31:19,010 --> 00:31:22,530
if a person acts righteously
but also commits wrongs,

610
00:31:22,980 --> 00:31:25,860
is this person still righteous?

611
00:31:28,050 --> 00:31:29,860
All things follow the laws
of heaven and earth.

612
00:31:30,290 --> 00:31:31,530
If one goes against their conscience,

613
00:31:32,380 --> 00:31:33,860
no matter how many good deeds they do,

614
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:37,330
they will face divine retribution.

615
00:31:49,050 --> 00:31:50,380
I believe

616
00:31:50,770 --> 00:31:52,860
you're a person who acts uprightly.

617
00:31:53,330 --> 00:31:56,090
Second Lady Jiang, the rain has stopped.

618
00:32:02,290 --> 00:32:03,010
I'll take my leave.

619
00:32:04,250 --> 00:32:05,420
Thank you

620
00:32:05,460 --> 00:32:06,980
for not minding talking with me.

621
00:32:07,860 --> 00:32:08,530
I'll take my leave now.

622
00:32:17,140 --> 00:32:19,810
I'll wash and return your clothes.

623
00:32:38,660 --> 00:32:45,820
[Nothing but Virtue]

624
00:33:01,260 --> 00:33:05,900
[Hanlin Academy]

625
00:33:18,420 --> 00:33:20,380
[Hanlin Academy]
What unpleasant encounter

626
00:33:20,460 --> 00:33:21,860
did you have to face
to end up like this?

627
00:33:25,660 --> 00:33:26,620
Duke Su,

628
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:27,860
why are you here?

629
00:33:29,730 --> 00:33:31,050
Your clothes

630
00:33:31,900 --> 00:33:32,620
look terrible.

631
00:33:33,770 --> 00:33:34,460
Come with me.

632
00:33:52,780 --> 00:33:56,420
[Hanlin Academy]

633
00:34:14,660 --> 00:34:15,350
Does it fit?

634
00:34:16,700 --> 00:34:19,790
Why don't you have women's clothes
at your place?

635
00:34:19,790 --> 00:34:21,540
You've asked about my background.

636
00:34:22,030 --> 00:34:23,100
Don't you know why?

637
00:34:23,140 --> 00:34:24,740
They say you don't like women.

638
00:34:26,700 --> 00:34:27,580
But why?

639
00:34:28,540 --> 00:34:29,620
Women are wonderful.

640
00:34:29,830 --> 00:34:31,060
They're caring

641
00:34:31,740 --> 00:34:32,580
and considerate.

642
00:34:32,620 --> 00:34:33,310
What about you?

643
00:34:35,350 --> 00:34:36,580
You're not getting any younger.

644
00:34:36,950 --> 00:34:38,220
You're the one who's getting older.

645
00:34:38,580 --> 00:34:40,310
I actually feel quite good

646
00:34:40,510 --> 00:34:42,060
living alone these days.

647
00:34:44,390 --> 00:34:46,100
No emotions to worry about

648
00:34:46,260 --> 00:34:47,350
and free to act.

649
00:34:47,470 --> 00:34:49,540
You're the one
who truly fits that description.

650
00:34:50,100 --> 00:34:51,060
Thank you for the compliment.

651
00:34:53,940 --> 00:34:55,870
But there's something I need
to remind you of.

652
00:34:56,100 --> 00:34:58,870
Getting close to Shen Yurong
is a risky move.

653
00:34:59,060 --> 00:35:00,140
I have to do it.

654
00:35:00,980 --> 00:35:01,910
I want to face him

655
00:35:02,510 --> 00:35:04,390
just like he faced Xue Fangfei
in her grave.

656
00:35:04,820 --> 00:35:05,980
I need to find his weakness

657
00:35:06,250 --> 00:35:07,980
to clear Xue Fangfei's name.

658
00:35:08,340 --> 00:35:09,170
What weakness?

659
00:35:09,340 --> 00:35:10,210
I haven't found it yet.

660
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:11,140
Over time,

661
00:35:11,140 --> 00:35:12,470
he will eventually slip.

662
00:35:16,460 --> 00:35:17,540
Have you considered the consequences?

663
00:35:18,140 --> 00:35:18,830
Xiao Heng,

664
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:20,950
you can be more frank.

665
00:35:22,060 --> 00:35:25,140
The retaliation from Eldest Princess
could cost me my life.

666
00:35:25,700 --> 00:35:27,030
And my all-or-nothing gamble

667
00:35:28,180 --> 00:35:29,830
might also be a path
to my own destruction.

668
00:35:30,340 --> 00:35:31,510
Admitting it

669
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:33,060
means you're afraid.

670
00:35:33,820 --> 00:35:36,060
Having fear is a good thing.

671
00:35:36,540 --> 00:35:39,790
I actually feel much lighter

672
00:35:40,740 --> 00:35:41,910
after talking to you.

673
00:35:42,460 --> 00:35:44,060
Do I also have a therapeutic effect?

674
00:35:44,380 --> 00:35:45,620
Anyway, I have nothing to lose.

675
00:35:47,980 --> 00:35:48,700
Have some chicken.

676
00:35:54,620 --> 00:35:55,660
Has Jiuyue returned?

677
00:35:55,860 --> 00:35:56,420
She was here.

678
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:57,180
But she left.

679
00:35:57,700 --> 00:35:59,790
Don't worry about Magistrate Xue
and that young lady.

680
00:36:00,060 --> 00:36:00,790
I'll remember.

681
00:36:01,060 --> 00:36:03,260
But you know what she's like.

682
00:36:03,420 --> 00:36:04,540
She acts too casually.

683
00:36:04,540 --> 00:36:05,790
I'm sorry to trouble you.

684
00:36:06,060 --> 00:36:07,430
You have to promise me one thing.

685
00:36:09,460 --> 00:36:11,030
No matter what plans you make,

686
00:36:11,980 --> 00:36:13,830
don't get yourself caught up in them.

687
00:36:16,180 --> 00:36:17,220
You may have nothing to lose.

688
00:36:20,220 --> 00:36:21,620
But it doesn't I can afford to lose it.

689
00:36:26,700 --> 00:36:27,310
All right.

690
00:36:34,620 --> 00:36:35,220
It's burnt.

691
00:36:41,620 --> 00:36:42,910
Yurong, where were you?

692
00:36:44,740 --> 00:36:45,540
At Hanlin Academy.

693
00:36:46,140 --> 00:36:48,310
The task of editing the classics
is really hectic these days.

694
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:49,660
Stop lying.

695
00:36:50,820 --> 00:36:52,820
Your sister told me everything
when she got back.

696
00:36:54,900 --> 00:36:55,650
Tonight,

697
00:36:56,690 --> 00:36:58,820
were you with Jiang Li?

698
00:37:01,820 --> 00:37:02,460
No.

699
00:37:03,290 --> 00:37:05,650
You still don't understand
the seriousness of this matter.

700
00:37:05,980 --> 00:37:08,380
Have you forgotten
the suffering our family went through?

701
00:37:09,020 --> 00:37:09,540
Father,

702
00:37:10,100 --> 00:37:11,500
I will avenge you.

703
00:37:12,060 --> 00:37:15,250
You may take revenge
on this corrupt official.

704
00:37:15,660 --> 00:37:20,020
But there will be others to oppress us.

705
00:37:22,060 --> 00:37:25,460
Unless you become an official,

706
00:37:26,220 --> 00:37:29,210
or else not only will you fail
to take revenge,

707
00:37:29,820 --> 00:37:35,130
but you'll also bring trouble
to our family.

708
00:37:35,820 --> 00:37:36,570
Don't worry.

709
00:37:36,940 --> 00:37:38,130
I will study hard

710
00:37:38,860 --> 00:37:39,860
and become a top scholar.

711
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:42,610
Then I'll be a good official

712
00:37:43,020 --> 00:37:45,340
and eradicate all corrupt ones
who oppress the people.

713
00:37:46,220 --> 00:37:46,910
Have you forgotten

714
00:37:47,220 --> 00:37:49,510
your promise to your father
on his deathbed

715
00:37:49,740 --> 00:37:52,140
and how difficult it was
to get to where you are now?

716
00:37:53,350 --> 00:37:54,180
Do you think

717
00:37:55,740 --> 00:37:59,390
Eldest Princess will be pleased

718
00:38:00,140 --> 00:38:02,220
if she finds out

719
00:38:02,220 --> 00:38:03,260
you are associating
with Second Lady Jiang,

720
00:38:03,350 --> 00:38:04,350
who looks just like Xue Fangfei?

721
00:38:05,430 --> 00:38:06,580
They are not the same person.

722
00:38:07,220 --> 00:38:08,790
Mother, stop mixing them up.

723
00:38:08,870 --> 00:38:10,540
Is that the point?

724
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:12,140
Does my opinion matter?

725
00:38:12,140 --> 00:38:15,660
The point is the princess believes
she's Xue Fangfei.

726
00:38:16,140 --> 00:38:17,740
Think about your grand ambitions.

727
00:38:17,820 --> 00:38:19,540
Think about how our family's good life

728
00:38:19,540 --> 00:38:20,790
was earned.

729
00:38:20,980 --> 00:38:21,660
Yurong,

730
00:38:21,860 --> 00:38:23,910
do not play with fire.

731
00:38:24,060 --> 00:38:25,460
Mother, you don't need to remind me.

732
00:38:25,730 --> 00:38:26,570
I know the path

733
00:38:27,340 --> 00:38:28,420
I need to take better than anyone.

734
00:38:41,730 --> 00:38:42,570
My Lord,

735
00:38:42,820 --> 00:38:43,940
you won't believe it.

736
00:38:44,540 --> 00:38:46,020
But being poisoned

737
00:38:46,460 --> 00:38:47,690
felt quite fascinating.

738
00:38:48,380 --> 00:38:51,820
I saw beautiful women around me.

739
00:38:52,380 --> 00:38:55,090
I just hugged them all.

740
00:38:55,250 --> 00:38:55,900
Then I...

741
00:38:57,860 --> 00:38:59,820
Then let Jiuyue catch another snake
to bite you again.

742
00:38:59,860 --> 00:39:00,650
No, no.

743
00:39:00,900 --> 00:39:02,380
I was just joking.

744
00:39:15,730 --> 00:39:17,020
Is she drunk?

745
00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:18,340
How much did she drink?

746
00:39:22,220 --> 00:39:23,540
It's wine mixed with scorpion venom.

747
00:39:23,700 --> 00:39:24,220
Too strong.

748
00:39:25,540 --> 00:39:26,020
Perfect.

749
00:39:27,260 --> 00:39:28,740
Keep her confined at the residence

750
00:39:29,180 --> 00:39:30,580
until the Great Zhao delegation arrives.

751
00:39:33,980 --> 00:39:34,650
Wen Ji,

752
00:39:35,060 --> 00:39:36,090
take her to her room.

753
00:39:36,580 --> 00:39:37,060
Lu Ji,

754
00:39:37,500 --> 00:39:38,380
come with me to the wine shop.

755
00:39:38,820 --> 00:39:39,250
Yes, My Lord.

756
00:39:39,420 --> 00:39:40,940
Isn't Lu Ji holding on to her?

757
00:39:41,100 --> 00:39:42,500
Let Lu Ji take her inside.

758
00:39:42,500 --> 00:39:44,060
Now that you're no longer poisoned,

759
00:39:44,380 --> 00:39:45,570
you can continue watching over her.

760
00:39:46,580 --> 00:39:47,020
I...

761
00:39:53,900 --> 00:39:54,900
You...

762
00:39:56,300 --> 00:39:57,690
No, stop.

763
00:40:09,900 --> 00:40:10,980
Let me out!

764
00:40:11,300 --> 00:40:12,020
Someone!

765
00:40:12,250 --> 00:40:13,300
Someone!

766
00:40:13,530 --> 00:40:14,380
Am I not someone?

767
00:40:15,020 --> 00:40:15,690
Wait there.

768
00:40:15,980 --> 00:40:17,500
Before the Great Zhao delegation arrives,

769
00:40:17,610 --> 00:40:18,460
you're not going anywhere.

770
00:40:18,650 --> 00:40:19,300
You wouldn't dare.

771
00:40:19,980 --> 00:40:21,530
I have never been locked up
since I was a child.

772
00:40:22,020 --> 00:40:23,980
You better let me go now.

773
00:40:24,570 --> 00:40:25,730
Or else...

774
00:40:31,940 --> 00:40:32,690
Or else...

775
00:40:34,420 --> 00:40:35,530
Or else what?

776
00:40:37,500 --> 00:40:37,900
Wen Ji,

777
00:40:38,500 --> 00:40:39,340
what are you trying to do?

778
00:40:43,530 --> 00:40:45,610
I've already prepared myself.

779
00:40:45,980 --> 00:40:47,250
Don't think you can poison me again.

780
00:40:47,730 --> 00:40:48,420
Anyway,

781
00:40:48,780 --> 00:40:51,860
you're not stepping out
of the Duke's Residence today.

782
00:40:52,820 --> 00:40:54,900
Wen Ji, how dare you!

783
00:40:55,570 --> 00:40:56,380
Just stay put.

784
00:40:56,460 --> 00:40:57,300
Don't even think about leaving.

785
00:41:00,940 --> 00:41:02,300
I need to go to the Ye's Residence.

786
00:41:03,300 --> 00:41:04,130
Didn't Xiao Heng ask me

787
00:41:04,130 --> 00:41:05,610
to treat Magistrate Xue?

788
00:41:06,090 --> 00:41:08,210
I need to treat him. I have to go now.

789
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,250
Do you think I'll fall for that?

790
00:41:13,090 --> 00:41:14,900
You better get it straight.

791
00:41:15,860 --> 00:41:16,900
Xiao Heng even went spider hunting

792
00:41:16,900 --> 00:41:18,650
with me to convince me

793
00:41:19,050 --> 00:41:21,380
to treat Magistrate Xue.

794
00:41:22,050 --> 00:41:23,340
And you should know

795
00:41:23,900 --> 00:41:25,980
what Jiang Li means to him, right?

796
00:41:26,530 --> 00:41:29,500
If Magistrate Xue isn't treated in time,

797
00:41:30,050 --> 00:41:31,610
it'll be all your fault.

798
00:41:31,980 --> 00:41:32,820
And

799
00:41:33,730 --> 00:41:36,980
it won't be
a few military punishments anymore.

800
00:41:47,460 --> 00:41:50,460
[Jinsi Hall]

801
00:41:50,460 --> 00:41:51,250
Who are you?

802
00:41:51,820 --> 00:41:53,340
I'm here to treat Magistrate Xue.

803
00:41:54,570 --> 00:41:54,980
You can't come in.

804
00:41:55,940 --> 00:41:57,500
You're trespassing.

805
00:41:57,820 --> 00:41:59,020
I can report you to the authorities.

806
00:41:59,610 --> 00:42:00,250
Official Ye,

807
00:42:00,420 --> 00:42:01,820
we're here on Duke Su's orders

808
00:42:01,820 --> 00:42:03,020
to treat Magistrate Xue.

809
00:42:03,530 --> 00:42:04,730
Second Lady Jiang knows about this.

810
00:42:05,130 --> 00:42:06,300
You work for Duke Su.

811
00:42:06,900 --> 00:42:07,650
You know him, right?

812
00:42:07,980 --> 00:42:09,300
Can I go in now?

813
00:42:09,530 --> 00:42:10,130
No, you cannot.

814
00:42:10,500 --> 00:42:12,210
Jiang Li didn't tell me about this.

815
00:42:12,420 --> 00:42:13,780
Let me inform her first.

816
00:42:14,020 --> 00:42:15,300
No need for you two to worry.

817
00:42:17,340 --> 00:42:18,420
I get it.

818
00:42:19,900 --> 00:42:21,210
He doesn't like Xiao Heng, right?

819
00:42:21,460 --> 00:42:22,340
Watch your words.

820
00:42:22,650 --> 00:42:23,570
Can you be more subtle?

821
00:42:23,940 --> 00:42:24,900
His Lordship

822
00:42:25,170 --> 00:42:26,530
just doesn't want to deal with him.

823
00:42:26,570 --> 00:42:27,300
Excuse me,

824
00:42:28,210 --> 00:42:28,900
please watch your words.

825
00:42:29,250 --> 00:42:31,050
Stop beating around the bush.

826
00:42:31,500 --> 00:42:33,500
Are you letting me in or not?

827
00:42:33,530 --> 00:42:34,020
No.

828
00:42:34,380 --> 00:42:35,300
You're not, huh?

829
00:42:35,530 --> 00:42:36,420
Ye Shijie, don't provoke her.

830
00:42:37,090 --> 00:42:37,690
She will...

831
00:42:46,130 --> 00:42:46,980
Keep an eye on him.

832
00:42:47,500 --> 00:42:48,500
I'm going in to do the treatment.

833
00:42:51,020 --> 00:42:52,050
Stop right there!

834
00:42:52,420 --> 00:42:53,170
It's wise

835
00:42:53,340 --> 00:42:54,090
