836
00:43:01,780 --> 00:43:02,130
You...

837
00:43:02,860 --> 00:43:03,300
You...

838
00:43:06,460 --> 00:43:07,210
Don't touch him!

839
00:43:11,420 --> 00:43:12,050
You're welcome.

840
00:43:14,340 --> 00:43:15,210
His illness

841
00:43:15,900 --> 00:43:16,420
isn't easy to treat.

842
00:43:16,980 --> 00:43:17,570
Wait.

843
00:43:18,020 --> 00:43:19,420
Where did this quack come from?

844
00:43:19,650 --> 00:43:20,940
Who gives you the permission
to touch Magistrate Xue?

845
00:43:35,170 --> 00:43:36,530
Where am I?

846
00:43:37,460 --> 00:43:38,860
I'm the only one
who can treat his illness.

847
00:43:39,090 --> 00:43:40,860
But it can't be cured in one day.

848
00:43:41,570 --> 00:43:42,130
If the poison...

849
00:43:45,130 --> 00:43:46,300
I mean if medicine is too strong,

850
00:43:46,570 --> 00:43:47,900
it could be fatal.

851
00:43:48,130 --> 00:43:50,170
So I will come once a day.

852
00:43:50,570 --> 00:43:51,820
If you have questions,

853
00:43:52,090 --> 00:43:53,650
you can just ask Jiang Li.

854
00:43:54,690 --> 00:43:55,210
Wen Ji,

855
00:43:55,530 --> 00:43:56,380
take him outside.

856
00:43:57,300 --> 00:43:58,820
The poison for the next treatment
is highly toxic.

857
00:43:59,250 --> 00:43:59,940
So you better stay away.

858
00:44:00,130 --> 00:44:00,780
I'm not leaving.

859
00:44:03,090 --> 00:44:04,690
Do you think
you don't look pathetic enough?

860
00:44:13,460 --> 00:44:14,460
Give me the antidote!

861
00:44:14,460 --> 00:44:15,210
I can walk myself out!

862
00:44:22,780 --> 00:44:24,460
Can you give me the antidote first?

863
00:44:25,420 --> 00:44:26,420
What's the rush?

864
00:44:26,730 --> 00:44:28,500
She'll give it to you
after the treatment.

865
00:44:42,380 --> 00:44:42,900
Wen Ji!

866
00:44:45,050 --> 00:44:45,980
Give me the antidote!

867
00:45:14,530 --> 00:45:15,250
Find Xiao Heng.

868
00:45:24,050 --> 00:45:24,900
Why didn't you catch it?

869
00:45:40,500 --> 00:45:41,170
Don't just stand there!

870
00:45:41,170 --> 00:45:41,940
Find His Lordship!

871
00:45:42,090 --> 00:45:43,130
The antidote.

872
00:45:47,530 --> 00:45:47,980
Open your mouth!

873
00:45:53,380 --> 00:45:54,130
His Lordship is at the wine shop.

874
00:46:26,170 --> 00:46:27,500
Just surrender now.

875
00:46:28,020 --> 00:46:29,650
You're no match for me.

876
00:46:31,050 --> 00:46:33,980
Do you think you can last
until Xiao Heng gets here?

877
00:46:34,210 --> 00:46:34,940
Him?

878
00:46:35,820 --> 00:46:36,900
He's no match for me...

879
00:46:40,940 --> 00:46:41,940
We can only take a chance.

880
00:46:41,980 --> 00:46:42,650
What are you planning to do?

881
00:46:56,130 --> 00:46:59,210
This thing seems to be effective.

882
00:47:02,860 --> 00:47:03,780
But why do I feel

883
00:47:04,460 --> 00:47:06,380
that I'm also...

884
00:47:32,580 --> 00:47:38,060
♪If there are no happy memories♪

885
00:47:40,180 --> 00:47:45,660
♪How can we traverse
the forbidden land of sorrow?♪

886
00:47:47,460 --> 00:47:53,540
♪Two cold and unfeeling bodies♪

887
00:47:54,220 --> 00:48:01,500
♪Holding hands,
can we get through the snow season?♪

888
00:48:02,540 --> 00:48:09,020
♪In the cold wind, in the long night♪

889
00:48:09,820 --> 00:48:16,100
♪Embracing the remaining warmth♪

890
00:48:17,380 --> 00:48:24,620
♪The depth of the sea, unfathomable♪

891
00:48:24,700 --> 00:48:30,700
♪Can it bury yesterday's sighs?♪

892
00:48:31,380 --> 00:48:37,420
♪Continue to love,
cherishing it with my life♪

893
00:48:39,260 --> 00:48:45,980
♪Continue to live,
even with only a glimmer of hope♪

894
00:48:47,100 --> 00:48:53,900
♪Whether in sorrow or joy,
I believe in you♪

895
00:48:54,900 --> 00:49:00,820
♪I'd rather be trapped
in the world's extremes♪

896
00:49:01,540 --> 00:49:08,660
♪Continue to live,
exhausting all courage♪

897
00:49:08,900 --> 00:49:16,180
♪Continue to love,
until the breath runs out♪

898
00:49:17,060 --> 00:49:23,860
♪Traversing half a lifetime
of loneliness, just to meet you♪

899
00:49:24,460 --> 00:49:30,900
♪After the hardships,
never to part again♪

